# CVE-2026-42496: perl-Archive-Tar path traversal via crafted symlinks.
# fix_deferred by Debian; no patch available. Only exploitable when
# extracting untrusted tar archives with Archive-Tar — our Python app
# never invokes Perl tar extraction.
CVE-2026-42496

# CVE-2026-8376: perl heap buffer overflow in regex compilation.
# Only exploitable on 32-bit builds. Our ECS target is ARM64 (64-bit).
CVE-2026-8376

# CVE-2026-58016: glib integer underflow in gio/gdbusintrospection.c via
# g_dbus_node_info_new_for_xml. No fix available. App doesn't parse D-Bus
# introspection XML at runtime.
CVE-2026-58016

# CVE-2026-13221: perl-base regex compilation silently incorrect results.
# No fix version available. Our Python app never invokes perl regexes.
CVE-2026-13221
